headline: Devon Energy to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in Store This Season?
summary: DVN heads into Q4 earnings with estimates pointing to lower revenues and profit. DVN is set to report Q4 results on Feb. 17, with the consensus mark for EPS at 86 cents, down 25.9% Y/Y.

headline: Why are Devon, Expand Energy both moving to Houston? OKC company moves, explained.
summary: Two major energy companies, Devon Energy and Expand Energy, are moving teams from Oklahoma City to Houston. Here's a look into the shifts.
